<h3><a name="development"></a>Development</h3>

<p>As a version control system for its source code, w2do uses <a href="http://git-scm.com/" title="the fast version control system">Git</a> with a public repositories located on <a href="http://gitorious.org/" title="free open source project hosting">Gitorious</a>. To download the latest development version of any of the utilities, you can either use one of the following commands:</p>

<pre>git clone git://gitorious.org/w2do/mainline.git w2do
git clone git://gitorious.org/w2do/lite2do.git lite2do
git clone git://gitorious.org/w2do/lite2do-irssi.git lite2do-irssi</pre>

<p>or you can explore the repository tree directly in your browser:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="http://gitorious.org/w2do/mainline/trees/master">w2do repository tree</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://gitorious.org/w2do/lite2do/trees/master">lite2do repository tree</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://gitorious.org/w2do/lite2do-irssi/trees/master">lite2do-irssi repository tree</a></li>
</ul>
